Akamai Technologies Inc (AKAM) CEO F Thomson Leighton Bought $999,768 of Shares


July 17, 2017, 10:15:01 AM EDT
By insider, GuruFocus









































Shutterstock photo


CEO of Akamai Technologies Inc ( AKAM ) F Thomson Leighton bought 19,817 shares of AKAM on 07/14/2017 at an average price of $50.45 a share. The total cost of this purchase was $999,768.Akamai Technologies Inc is a United States based company which provides cloud services for delivering, optimizing and securing online content and business applications. Akamai Technologies Inc has a market cap of $8.75 billion; its shares were traded at around $50.62 with a P/E ratio of 27.66 and P/S ratio of 3.73. Akamai Technologies Inc had annual average EBITDA growth of 17.00% over the past ten years. GuruFocus rated Akamai Technologies Inc the business predictability rank of 5-star .CEO Recent Trades:CEO F Thomson Leighton bought 19,817 shares of AKAM stock on 07/14/2017 at the average price of $50.45. The price of the stock has increased by 0.34% since.click here

. 

